title: Momo Wholefood
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Organic, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Gluten-free, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A warm and friendly cafe serving breakfast and lunch. Located within Organic Feast, an organic grocery store. Serves primarily vegetarian food with plenty of options for vegans. Raw and gluten free available. Has a juice bar. Makes vegan salads daily in-house. Desserts include brownies, pecan pie and raspberry cheesecake (all raw, vegan and gluten free).
